parameters.name: mms3_des_dist_fast1_movie
parameters.description: ---> Movie - 11.6 eV. This variable is a 'virtual' variable that is computed using the function alternate_view (see https://cdaweb.gsfc.nasa.gov/pub/software/cdawlib/source/virtual_funcs.pro) on the with inputs of the variables ['mms3_des_dist_fast'].
